    <h3 class="text-center">About Chatbot Project</h3>
    <div style="color: rgb(209, 245, 224);">

        This is a simple JavaScript-based chatbot that provides automated responses based on predefined messages stored in a JSON file. The bot processes user input, matches it against the dataset, and returns relevant responses. If the input is not recognized, it responds with a default message. The project includes:
        <br><br>
        <b>Message Handling:</b> User input is matched case-insensitively and trimmed for more accurate responses. <br>
        <b>Asynchronous Fetching:</b> The bot retrieves predefined messages from a JSON file. <br>
        <b>Interactive UI:</b> User messages and bot responses are displayed dynamically within a chat interface. <br>
        <b>Input Validation:</b> Prevents sending empty messages. <br>
        <b>Custom Animations:</b> Smooth transitions when displaying bot responses. <br>
        This chatbot can serve as a starting point for a more advanced AI chatbot system. <br>
